data.description: Back on market due to buyers financing. Attention investors!  This is your chance to own a fully operational and fully booked out short term rental.  A rare find located in one of the most desirable neighborhoods of Seminole Heights.  The first thing that you notice is the charm and historical features.  Both units feature hardwood floors to high ceilings, covered porches, lots of natural light and the amazing curb appeal.  One unit, is a one bedroom one bath. The other unit is a two bedroom, one bath, and each unit has their own laundry room. This will not last long!  Come start, or add to your portfolio!
